tika.dc.description:
Nathan Bailey is on the run. Not only is he the target of a nationwide manhunt—he’s the prey of a savage hit man. 

Nathan is twelve-years-old, with no one to turn to. He already knows life is unfair, and that to survive he has only himself, his smarts, and his honesty to depend on. But will that be enough as he takes flight into a terrifying world that has branded him a killer—and is waiting at every turn to destroy him?
tika.dc.subject: USA
